Project description:
This project included the implementation of inheritance and polymorphism, design patterns including factory and singleton, data-driven programming and a tracker framework.  
I drawing is called Space Adventures. 

Where I got my sprites: 
I drew the sprites using inkspace and GIMP. The following were used as references/inspirations. 
Astronaut:
https://d2gg9evh47fn9z.cloudfront.net/800px_COLOURBOX7024296.jpg
