What sprite did I create (not Sprite or MultiSprite):
I created 3 sprites: 
1) Rotating astronaut with 24 frames
2) UFO with 2 frames
3) Rocket with 6 frames. This is a two way multisprite where 3 frames go right and 3 go left. 

The easiest part of this project:
1) Converting the ranged for loops to while loops and vice versa. 

Problems that I had in completing this project:
